# Essential Project Plan

Answer these key questions to plan a software engineering project

### Essential Project Plan
* Requirements
* Design
* Code
* Test


### Requirements
* Time
* Money
* Function
* Priorities - Time, Money, Function
* Top 10 objectives
* Customer interactions


### Design
* Pages
* Page layout
* Content creation
* Visual appearance


### Code
* Code milestones
* Reuse plan
* Learning plan
* Schedule


### Test
* Acceptance criteria
* Issue tracking
* Reviews
* Release criteria
